title: Airstrike on Dnipro apartment block injures five - as two Russian cities rocked by blasts
description: At least nine people have been hurt after two buildings were hit by blasts in the Ukrainian city of Dnipro.

title: India's first openly gay prince says parents wanted  him to have 'conversion brain surgery'

title: Ministry of Defence accidentally sends classified information to Kremlin ally
